A4.text: Recorded by singer and actor Elvis Presley, it was part of the album, Blue Hawaii (1961), the soundtrack to the movie Blue Hawaii.

A5.text: An uptempo version by Andy Williams peaked at No. 3 in the UK Singles Chart in March 1970.
